    • 构造器详细资料

      • ProjectFlatJoinFunction

        private ProjectFlatJoinFunction(int[] fields,
                                boolean[] isFromFirst,
                                R outTupleInstance)
        Instantiates and configures a ProjectJoinFunction. Creates output tuples by copying fields of joined input tuples (or a full input object) into an output tuple.
        参数:
        fields - List of indexes fields that should be copied to the output tuple. If the full input object should be copied (for example in case of a non-tuple input) the index should be -1.
        isFromFirst - List of flags indicating whether the field should be copied from the first (true) or the second (false) input.
        outTupleInstance - An instance of an output tuple.

        从接口复制的说明: FlatJoinFunction
        The join method, called once per joined pair of elements.
        指定者:
        join 在接口中 FlatJoinFunction<T1,T2,R extends Tuple>
        指定者:

        参数:
        in1 - The element from first input.
        in2 - The element from second input.
        out - The collector used to return zero, one, or more elements.
